{"tid":1516310,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同家人嗌交 想取下暖","createTime":"2019-08-29T13:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T14:53:35.000Z","uid":72839,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2fc5e7dafaf186fed6fd922607888d0236663fbf","tid":1516310,"uid":72839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:54:10.000Z","msg":"都唔洗點詳述啦，最近應該大家都經歷過<br />\n其實我feel到屋企人都有儘量避開呢啲話題，但今日始終都係忍唔住<br />\n我唔會怪佢哋，我屋企人學歷唔高，捱咗好多年先叫做勉強有安定啲嘅生活<br />\n本身以為自己可以忍住唔出聲，但聽到佢哋咁講被濫捕虐待嘅手足都真係吞唔落啖氣<br />\n預咗改變唔到佢哋，只係有啲嘢唔可以唔出聲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想要攬攬"},{"pid":"d74085b9b44702ddcc8fad399aae6c35deb6e230","tid":1516310,"uid":175159,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:56:02.000Z","msg":"攬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arsqpGE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FarsqpGE.jpg&h=df7beaa0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1447ee8eb6de38a0985b66b3d06777e096ab45c","tid":1516310,"uid":109047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:56:33.000Z","msg":"想攬你"},{"pid":"80438ca2cf9f365045c3dc5e7768810ddbb2309f","tid":1516310,"uid":279236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:56:44.000Z","msg":"攬實<br />\n利申大隻巴"},{"pid":"078b882d04b22fcf9b1b8f5b12779b556ec4aa86","tid":1516310,"uid":39245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:57:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c42369fff4640360a32809d54b5545fb15464c2","tid":1516310,"uid":267822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">攬實你</span>"},{"pid":"b43f52e837914aec6c84e8260be1c62e5bd0ce8e","tid":151631